{"prompt": "Generate a website for a freelance design agency. The website should be corporate and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Stellar Designs - Creative Solutions</title>\n    <style>\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            color: #333;\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: auto;\n            overflow: hidden;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n        header {\n            background-color: #00529B;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding-top: 30px;\n            min-height: 70px;\n            border-bottom: #00529B 3px solid;\n            text-align: center;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            padding-bottom: 10px;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n        header p {\n            font-size: 1.1em;\n            color: #e0e0e0;\n        }\n        #main-content {\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n        #main-content h2 {\n            color: #00529B;\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n        .service-item {\n            display: inline-block;\n            width: 30%;\n            margin: 15px 1.5%;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .service-item:hover {\n            transform: translateY(-10px);\n            box-shadow: 0 12px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);\n        }\n        .service-item h3 {\n            color: #00529B;\n            margin-top: 0;\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n        }\n        footer {\n            background-color: #003366;\n            color: #fff;\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            font-size: 0.9em;\n            box-shadow: 0 -2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n        }\n        footer a {\n            color: #add8e6;\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n        .contact-form {\n            margin-top: 30px;\n            padding: 20px;\n            background-color: #fff;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);\n            display: inline-block;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n        .contact-form input, .contact-form textarea {\n            width: calc(100% - 20px);\n            padding: 10px;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            border: 1px solid #ccc;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n        }\n        .contact-form button {\n            background-color: #00529B;\n            color: #fff;\n            padding: 12px 20px;\n            border: none;\n            border-radius: 4px;\n            cursor: pointer;\n            font-size: 1em;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n        .contact-form button:hover {\n            background-color: #003366;\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Stellar Designs</h1>\n            <p>Transforming visions into stunning digital realities.</p>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <div class=\"container\" id=\"main-content\">\n        <h2>Our Services</h2>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Web Design</h3>\n            <p>Crafting modern, responsive, and user-friendly websites tailored to your brand.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>Branding & Identity</h3>\n            <p>Creating memorable logos, style guides, and brand assets that resonate.</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"service-item\">\n            <h3>UI/UX Design</h3>\n            <p>Designing intuitive interfaces and seamless user experiences that delight your audience.</p>\n        </div>\n\n        <div class=\"container contact-form\">\n            <h2>Get in Touch</h2>\n            <form action=\"#\" method=\"post\">\n                <input type=\"text\" name=\"name\" placeholder=\"Your Name\" required>\n                <input type=\"email\" name=\"email\" placeholder=\"Your Email\" required>\n                <textarea name=\"message\" rows=\"5\" placeholder=\"Your Message\" required></textarea>\n                <button type=\"submit\">Send Message</button>\n            </form>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Stellar Designs. All rights reserved. | <a href=\"#contact\">Contact Us</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n"}